{
  "texts": [
    "Using the adversarial autoencoder, a normative model is created.",
    "RVM with a linear kernel is utilized to perform classification analysis.",
    "This model is built with TensorFlow and sklearn_rvm packages.",
    "In most situations, the classifiers outperformed the normative method in terms of mean performance.",
    "Although traditional classifiers performed better in certain circumstances, the obtained difference is not Statistically reliable in most of the of cases."
  ]
}